No. 75/CF/52.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA,
CABINET SECRETARIAT.
New Delhi, the 20th September, 1956.
To
The undersigned is directed to inform Members of
the Council of Ministers that Shri Surendra Kumar Dey
assumed office as Minister with effect from today, the
20th September, 1956 (afternoon). He will hold charge of the
newly created Ministry of Community Development.
